casebody.head_matter:
Jack H. JONES
v.
KELLEY, Dir., AR DOC, et al.
No. 16A1028.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 24, 2017.
The application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice Alito and by him referred to the Court is denied.
Justice SOTOMAYOR, dissenting from the denial of the application for stay.
I dissent for the reasons set out in McGehee v. Hutchinson, 581 U.S. ----, --- S.Ct. ----, --- L.Ed.2d ----, 2017 WL 1414915 (2017) (Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
